summary: Hi! I saw your post asking about favorite phannie songs and I wasn't sure if you were just wanting stuff like always by erasure...
question: Hi! I saw your post asking about favorite phannie songs and I wasn't sure if you were just wanting stuff like always by erasure and interrupted by fireworks and stuff, but songs that always remind me of them are you picked me - a fine frenzy, falling away with you - muse, how they want me to be - best coast, all my life - nizlopi, and I found - amber run. I hope that one of these are helpful! I can't wait to see how your edit comes out!
answer: These are all great! My plan is to take song requests that remind people of phan and turn them into short, perhaps 30 second to 1 minute edits, like with clips of dnp and stuff. Hope that clears things up:)
